transcription: Hello sir, this is Mr.Gotham Yes Kumara? I think you called me Yes i did You told that the negotiation will be with Bajaju Finser Yeah yeah we have a 595 option for bhajajo fins on our schedule and how we apply for RERA. They will ask you to call me. I am calling you because basically, You have doubts regarding loan eligibility. My Loan Eligibility is 80 Lakhs maximum How much money can they fund? Basically how many days are there in the take home salary sir ? 82000 per month Sir we So you can add any other co-applicant? No I cannot do that sir. Ok so we have a low cost of loan for this amount. It will be around 70 lakhs to 80 maximum. They said that they will re-apply after 12 and half years, so we can fund 90%% or 80 % of the loan eligibility then there should be 1.8 lakhs as take-out salary and obligations Then only you can become an eligible customer for both 80 & 95%. There are no obligation? Yes but now loans have come in very low price so since they came at a lower cost will it help us with payments again? What did he mean by Self Payment ? If we want to get a 1.5 lakhs or 150 crore Lakh Loan in which IIT Lac is also available Can you again sell it for remaining 5 lakhs. I will ask you that, if its 40 then we could do it. If 10% of your money comes to us initially in this world If their income has increased Then we can increase our eligibility to get loans. Apart from that what other sources of revenue do you have? I don't know. My dad can also help me with that, but not much for my father. We are getting very less loans now. So what is your father doing? He owns a jewellery shop. It's for business profile. How much will you pay per year sir ? I don't have an idea, it depends on my job Yes, I have. How much do you earn every year? You can find out how it is. It depends on your father's income and the applicant's one. If Bajaji wants to make a business profile or an employee, he has other banks like HDFC etc.. I think that was out about it and find out how many years your father has been working in IT field? Do they have any EMI or something like that which he saw last 3years of his life ? Ok

transcription: Hello Sir, Hi sir. Good evening I am Sajjan from ASBL Spectra Financial District Tell me Are you looking for any 3BH apartments in the financial district? Yes sir Call us if there is a point extended. Sir i'm talking from Ashoka Builders Ok yes sir to ISB Road. Is it near Vipro circle or where is that place? We will cross the vippero cycle and then we come to Varanmot double 210 & triple 220 for these sizes based on East-West ratio of all buildings. Total handover will be done by December 2025 Total Propriet Handover is in December 2025. How many acres are these floors? This total 785 Acres and 4 Towers, plus 39 Vs The number of units for this floor was 1186 So it's a complete 3BHK Our special feature on our projects were the Balcony We focused more towards more because we are accepting 9x11 as a side for our balconies. So, what's your special concept? Just wait in line for one minute. Actually you guys shared brochure with me but I couldn't do that and came from ASBL only right ? Yes few units remaining is Asbl Spyre. Okay. Is the Spire also like that? Yes, it is a cockpit in Financial District How far does GAR campus from ASBL to SPIRE are getting prepared by November Why isn't this opening? You can check it out on our website I am not sure about that. When the business opens, what is your expectation for it? It's coming now! Is this area 3 Towers minutes from Vipro Junction to here. What are those big towers you have in this image? ACIC. They're building these huge Towers, right? That's our project now. Not that one... You gave us the ISB Road View below it, didn't ya? Yes! The ICAC Bank is looking at the map. How is the precious high field spot in tower? Now straight ISB, there was a new signal coming from that side. Yes That's right The same lefty sign came and it seems to be on our Right Side If you see one of those blue ones then its Varma I think thats what it looks like What Sir ? Open 3rd page of your profile. You can see Google banks in it, right? Yes If you zoom into ICICI bank and look at those high rise towers below them is a blue color one That property, office space. That's ISB Road No, it's 500-600 meters. It will be 1 and half kilometer from here. We have a right side project on the way This total 785 acres of land Where does that go straight ? There are 12 booths in Nanakram Where is this road going? It is 300m from Colgate. We took a U-turn at Mayamavatar and then we made our project in the next left for another less than three hundred meters I can understand now. Starting size is from 1980. We are getting more concentration in balcony than the other two. So we enjoyed the morning sun rise and evening sunset in our balcony. We gave a 9-11ft size to that concept of living room, And also provided bedroom sizes for it. Almost there is bedroom sized? Yes almost 3x7 type beds are available here This was actually one such concepts Our clubhouse has a very luxurious look Why did you give it square and not in corners? For the looks What do u mean by that? The balcony That's for elevation sir, to see outside It will be good a planter box here to keep plants and other things inside as well. Okay okay.. How much will sir it is a hybrid plant but you can keep as much height and size of your choice How many Feet will be our floor ? 10ft How is your planning? I have two plans. You only tell me, to settle down payments in one month. Or do we have the Loan Payment option and decide on how much of that will be paid out as per our needs Yes sir! So first thing here is 100% no repayments are required You know right, not every company has this kind offer One way would've been home loans Another possibility was if they were done by to the work progress of your organization. In this project, 30% of the 60 lakhs. These 6lakh should be paid now. Again sir in every 3-4 months or 5month we will complete each payment milestone slab I'll give an estimation for it In between those times from three 4 month's only after paying this is one option Or can go home loan If not, then we will give 3-4 months time and in between that period I'll make the payment That's right It would be done after paying for three month or fivemonths Yes How much amount does each installment cost? 10 lakhs per install. The flat cost of this unit was Rs2 Cr, so it will be 10% for the total price and 20 Lakh rupees in our case. What about 9080SFT ? All these together would make around two crores including AMMETIS , Base price and GST will be 2 crores. How much is the base Price? 84999 sir of limitations in units and we are having good places in this city. We have a direct outdoor view and sunrise views of the flats here. If we visit these sites once, I will show visit you. How many flats do you have? All of them are 1186. Is a swimming pool sufficient for so much people ? Yes, it is enough sir because everyone has their own area to swim in and they don't want the new arrivals having problems with that They will pay rent for the entire time, but they are not paying it. Will that be enough? Yes sir! Swimming pool is big and kids can play in there too they work from morning to evening and even at home. We are also doing something like clubhouse or MNTs but we should survey it first Why do you need swimming for us? For give indoor swimming pool, gym Supermarket, pharmacy and ATM 4 guest rooms Party hall 200k per system All these are necessary for everyone sir How did this supermarket tie up all of them? Sir! How does the super market tied it with what is happening here? That's more important giving one type of vendor as a pharmacy and we also give big vendors. Who gives bigger ones normally sir? No, no.. Bigger brands only. Pharmacy is still getting better at any time. That's our concept. Our our club, they are doing a big architect design for HP Luck and all celebrities like that too So we have already done such an architecture in two months drawings will be coming to us We have a site concept international contract based in Singapore. How much is this? SFT for Rs 8500 per sft It is ready to go up sir. Is it now? Yes, in November month. There are 15-18 flats available there What floor will you get from here Sir? Lower floors only. So below 7. It will be around 4-5% Okay okay. If everyone has a high rise then you can... You should also take some advantage of this because we have done investment in view for long term investments so when doing that taking the views as target would not hurt much since there are sunrises and sunset too right? Taking higher floors gives. Yes sir! Always use the high floor as we have 40 more and 20 plus is our current price point. Not even 25 but around 35% of this cost? We are available from 32nd Floor towards Outer Ring Road to Sunrise units etc.. Once in a while 27th or so can come directly at us. Is there any one like units in Spire. There are low rise apartments for this unit only Where do you live? I am Gachibowli, work-from home. Ok ok, so now do not go to your hometown? Yes sir, but since it is a workflow homie this time round we cannot come here. So did they plan for 25th or 27st today? We will be coming on the 24 th. That's what he said definitely! If i don't leave tomorrow morning then please remember that its Saturday morning, on 27th... Ok ok no problem. I'll come there. Please save this number and if any doubts call me then i can clear them for sure. Sure sir Thank You Sir If 100% payment is done here how much did they give? 8000.. How many were given in that amount? They gave 80000 finalized with the quoting price. You go home alone right? Yes Home Loan? I mean, we could pay that way only. Why did you take a particular plan for it when its about to be done at your place of work? Because if they do this then there is an offer which will run on interest reimbursement What's That ? Interest Reimbursements means If you want to get into bank loans and maximum 80% would come as Lone So 20 % So, from that 20%, only about ten percent is paid by booking advance. Another two years later we can give another 2-3 year payment for this provision. Not just twenty per cent but also a tenth of it and then again in next few months. Now what are doing to make them do so? we will do an agreement. After the Agreement, Bank disburses 80%. As I told earlier 20 % of work is done so first pay only this much but after that bank does a 40 lakhs. When you say this, it means that we are paying interest free be treating everyone as 3 ETS. Ok So your offer has been given a little bit? Sir basically why did I grant this Offer now continuous clients are coming to me 5-6 clients who rent out 5-6 times a day. So, when they go home and face problems... This is an additive moving project so it takes 2 12 years to get done. It's getting boring here as well. Yes! The offer runs for close of Rs1 point over. If we don't want the offers then at least give us extra discount if we don't have any offer. That's right, that is the thing. Sir let us discuss once and then you will get all details clearly Okay sir okay perfect yeah thank You sir! Did they sent it to me? Yes Sir! They have already done that. You can save this number and call us anytime if there are any further questions. What do we need these phone numbers for? I like ASP's number more than those phones. No no... Please use my college name now. OK Sir!! Thankyou so much Sir!!!

transcription: Hello, good afternoon sir. I am calling from ASBL Ok ok tell me Sir are you looking for a 3-bedroom apartment? Yes yes yes, of course So just some details When is the position here It will be in 2026 December. Okay, okay! Is there any delay than that or like next phase and second phases? Nothing much sir basically we handover from 2020 to 10th of Dec registration starts then so for filling up even if it it will be completed in 6 months buffer that's why 27-28 positions for us Okay, okay. Yeah so it is 2027? Yes! It will be 27th I guess. Because if your house gets a registration and they want us do interior work or else we need time for them then the process takes some more time because there are maximum 3-5 people in each day during this period of times so 894 apartments are available. When all these get registered & completed by 6 months only it would take about six month's to complete months to complete. Very good! Okay then tell me something else Yes sir What are flat sizes? Which size should be used for previous phase Basically there will 2 SFTs on total property One of and the other one 1870 Okay, understood Yes sir These 2 I have all property What about 3BHK or sft? Sir if we consider it as base price then 8500Rs per SFT sir If not all including GST and other restation everything included from 11th floor will be 1 crore 71 lakh rupees sir 1 point 7 Yes, plus you will also have a pre-mai scheme applicable to this too Oh okay! With whom do I need the money for it and with which bank are they associated ? Bajas Housing Pvt Ltd. Oh, BHFL? Yes sir! How much is the cash zone for Pre EMI 5 or 10% down payment? Here there will be a five percent payout You can choose as per your choice You may see if it's at least in that range Or you could do even ten-percent Down Payment Okay so now if I pay 5%, they will give 90%. And then again in the last year we have to repay it by paying only 50 %. Is that right? Yes sir basically how would this be done is there a different strategy here according RBI loans i changed my loan amount for your own money So at least 85 % of our debt goes into cash and remaining 7-10 percent 10%, 7th milestone. That means after 15 months only your pay is done? Oh! Okay understood. Yes sir approximately 20-25 January You can think of it as 25 Januari. Is there any Naavi in NBFC other than Bajaz we have only 3-4 banks and one is Bajaz housing HVAC has 25% down payment Axis Bank would be 10%. And then there's Quota account Ok, ok. Please share some details in my whatsapp once and I will talk to you later. If everything is good we can come tomorrow morning for a visit. Sure sir definitely. Do ASBL have any current ongoing projects on 26th December? No Sir! We are get Spectra in 20-25 December. This is same financialistic area also How much for SFT? It costs 9500 Rs per sft sir, it will be 1980 sq ft. It is going to cost till 2 crore 10 lakhs Okay okay I mean i do not want 2025 but 2026 days of certain details of what's happening? We'll send you the detailed information Sure Yes Sir yeah That said if there are any issues'll call you back on this one. Sure sir Thank You

No it's good this was first project They did commercial price for most The next one which we will see now So right You have done a residential project but the first one is now. Right, it's called as old and new Exactly sir What you need to see here When building any kind of projects It doesn't mean just walls or clubhouse But customer preference If we take all these into consideration Then this will be even more beneficial for your project. Yes! We can see everything and go ahead I have to find my driving factor Exactly It is not an easy investment You invested hard earned money in the property That's why like saying one time for us I will conclude if there comes to be best option Definitely Sir can come once today? What Time ? Anytime We stay till 6 30 Ok Your name My Name Is Sajjan Actually Sir, Our Sales Office We have moved from March 31st to Sheraton Hotel Where in the Exactly Because our location has been excluded So we are moving here since last two weeks We moved here from March 31st, 2 weeks back. How big is it sir ? 1800 to 2100 sq feet The ASB loft has exactly this loft. The total land parcel for you here lies at 490 acres We are considering two towers with G plus 45 floors You have 2 sizes 1695 and 1870 SFT These will be available to both East & West Spacings In total property, 76% of open space is available Our USP comes to outdoor per month including car parking amenities etc is approximately 1 point hr to 2 sqm. Ok yes Sir And another thing that you can do with this property handover comes in December 2026 Okay. You pay interest for that amount. We reimburse you 90% of the monthly loan, so if your disbursed money is 30k we will re-embrace it to a total rate 19%. That's how much ever monthly payment goes on. The entire G plus 45 has been completed till 3rd floor slab was finished So, this is the total structure of a terrestrial slab. Approximately, it will be done by 2025. In this timeline you are paying the amount to bank and we reimburse 90% of your debt If any one accumulates that money then approximately 8-10 lakhs is left for us You can use those amounts as a ratio your choice or you may even choose to have an interior. That is a benefit that we provide clients here. How much will be 8-10 lakhs till March? The percentage progress increases and so does disbursement. Accordingly, bank gives us money in terms of payment options but according 2 share properties they release 20% of the bank is released in that 40 lakhs. Then another 10%, then 60lakh and so on... So even after this progress it will increase your disbursement. You are saying only till March right? Next 2-3 months maybe. I am asking him how he is getting 3 months. So basically you pay 10% of the booking advance from your side and another 30th floor is completed then only we can give this flexibility to Bajaji. We will be able provide our offer with them How do they get interest? For example, for 20 lakhs bank You will forward that statement with our share and pay it back in this way. We are paying 90% of your amount at last month of the revenue from you. Yes! I understand why they give like this? Ok.. I understood that way to get more money. Basically many customers here belong first home buyers and buy their homes for a long time. They want EMI as well or house, it will be very difficult for many people. So we are running our offer in those areas. We run all the properties except one property here at Gachar and another on my upper floor as well called ASBL Springs & DCC. And also two other financial districts too have been ran by us over there. To give them a benefit of 3 months only ,we do runs these offers with clients. benefit. Where else in financial district? You can apply from 8 lakh rupees upto 10 Lakh and if 7Laks comes in that time period also even though I am doing SFT at Rs7likes but still there is not possible to get. But you are increasing 500 per500 per month. That is why i am asking We are done with 290 flats per solo type. 3 months. Then we recently did a price hike in this month to 9000 per sqft That's why I am asking, the property rate is not that fast anywhere else right? It increases by 100% sir if you see at your location it will increase every three years and then 500 more how much does one year later cost after 2 years? I am saying that because you bought it. Yes, yes..I was telling the same thing. I don't know whether they have or not but... I'm just stating there is a saturation and also asking if both will grow fast like this? It's in location sir as well. If we think about builder point of view then even next month it will be 9-10% or 10%. It doesn't impact us at all. People don' t even purchase. When there. It's a loss to builders So according with Market value sir price valuation will be done by Tatyapur and as per Inventory I am also going ahead Ok so this ASBL properties have been here since 30 years where did you build the ASBL properties from 30 years ago? We are not an Ashoka Builders. It is a commercial space and we have developed it in Hyderabad for about thirty-three years The owner of this building was Vijayabhaskar Reddy sir. transcription: Hello Sir, Good afternoon sir. Yeah who is this? My name Vijay and I am calling from ASBL Springs Pocharam project Okay You are looking for a 2BHK or 3 BHk purchase Yes sir We have done your enquiry right? We wanted to give some details about it. When our project comes we will provide the location and upal for that. Our projects are opposite of Singapore townships. If possible Raheja Minespace & Genpact is there in front of us meters distance, we will find Infosys Mega Campus Sir Okay And the exact location is 3 kilometers from here After crossing this area it's exit number 9 This is our of our project Sir, ASBL Springs Sir. As BL means Ashoka Builders India Private Limited Sir Okay Our total land for this Project 411 Acre Land Sir Ok In these four point one acre lands we have only two towers Sir ok These 2 Towers has G plus 14 floors here 2 towers total 478 units I will give you a short brief. When we get the SFT cost, it is 5000 per sft and if 2BHK comes to us then 69 lakhs sir including ofakh rupees In that amount of money if we exclude it from here then there are other charges like facility maintenance charge etc which will be accessed later on You will get access to them later. Another thing is, in this 69 the registration won't be included as per government requirement How much percentage? 7%-6%, according by Government Okay! For us how big would it cost for a flat you said that it will be 83, right sir Yes Sir. It's only Rs83 Ok then how many people are paying this amount? Yeah Sir Even if you send one rupee to them they would be in escrow account and the director shows to government. One more thing sir here is that customer benefit of India means whatever interest pay we book now 90% re-embedded from those interests every month For if you go for a loan and an EMI of 40k comes to your account We assume that there will be 30K interest in those 50 thousand rupees From the amount we get to us. When it's under construction... It has already been in Under Construction and we are handing over by September 2024. So until handover.. means till Sep 24th you're giving a handout. Even if I cut this much inside here, for interest amount also they'll reimburse it right? Yes sir. I don't have any other clarity to say about this We won' give till March 2024 Sir Ok ok So by march 20 24.. Is president offering like what he is doing now? No no sir We'll be giving it till March 2024, Sir Actually we have bought a flat in Vasavi group and want to try another one as well for rent Okay So what is the requirement? You will get interest benefit if you can just give us some money ASBL has this side of 12 acres right? Yes, our Deo Cheshar's house is at Okapet and Gajipoli Financial District. Ok, ok. Please put it there for me to see what you are saying is that till March 2024 the handover will be done? Yes sir September 2024 has been handed over as per RERA Now when we come into work progress 75% of our works have already completed We had G plus 14 floors right Sir In these Z Plus g-plus fourteen floor we completed the fourteen flooring labs and brickwork. Internal work is going on here sir Ok ok So next year September you will not come I took loan Sir If i put my name in that report then again it would be like this Sir confused sir I am getting Confused Sir I'm saying clearly it clearly. Project handover is September 2024 There will be an early handout but you have to make the offer for reimbursement of EMI right? For this girl's re-embursements we are planning till March 20 24 give it next year in March? Yes we will try but as per the R, you can't say that. Ok Sir, what is you asking? I will check if the Gachapalli is there. Ok Sir What about Uppalagiri ? Do they have it in gatcha pally too? The sales team overthere would be different from here We're other people here If any details need to details, I will transfer it to your contact list and they can reach out to us.achi bowly then there is spectra in financial district and when it comes 2cr starts up It will be handed over 6-1point 8 CR at start Okay..okay.. Sir there are different sizes There you have spiral spectra and 2BHKs only only 3 BHS will be available in the SPIRE and Spectra. I have premium three BHKS there. Okay. This sir about how to arrange a project like this? About my projects as well as these ones also know what i said If you want more details our team members call me Ok ok let see once that's called Spire & specter. OK! Then i'll do it in two days. Where are you working? In Hyderabad like this side.. Working as a CGA. Sir voice cut sorry about that. Here opposite to IKEA there is an Arbindo Galaxy right? Yes yes galaxy. We work on 7th floor overthere I will share the location and to sell our offer. Ashoka Billers has a brand and we want it sold accordingly. That's all I have for now regarding pricing or the offers Ok ok Thank You Sir, Have A Nice Day
